# Docker Dev

- Preferred dev: `npm run docker:dev` / `docker compose up --build`
- App port: **5173** — `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173`
- Services: `app` + `redis` only (no Mailpit)
- Inside compose, `REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379` is set automatically
- Rebuild after Dockerfile or dependency changes: `npm run docker:build`
- Hot reload: source is bind-mounted (`.:/app`); watchers use polling (`WATCHPACK_POLLING`, `CHOKIDAR_USEPOLLING`) for WSL2/Docker
- If edits are not picked up or pages show 500: `npm run docker:reset` (clears `.next` volume and rebuilds)
- Docker dev uses webpack (`dev:docker`), not Turbopack — more stable on WSL bind mounts

Do not document or default to port 3000 for this project.
